# Wealth Whisperer – AI-Powered Personal Finance Assistant

Wealth Whisperer is a prototype AI-driven financial planning tool tailored for the Irish market.  
It helps users make informed, tax-efficient investment and retirement decisions through:
- Personalized Risk Profiling (ML model based on behavioral finance)
- Retirement Planning (Monte Carlo simulations with Irish-specific tax and pension rules)
- Portfolio Allocation (asset class deep-dive with projected returns and tax simulations)
- ETF Explorer (real-time market data, risk metrics, and return forecasts)
- AI Chatbot (context-aware financial Q&A with RAG integration)

---

## Features
- Risk Profiling Quiz – Classifies users into Conservative, Balanced, or Aggressive profiles.
- Retirement Planner – Combines salary growth, contribution rates, and inflation-adjusted returns.
- Portfolio Simulator – Models equities, bonds, and cash with tax impact visualisation.
- ETF Calculator – Historical trends, volatility, Sharpe ratio, and Monte Carlo projections.
- AI Chatbot – Answers user-specific finance questions using Azure OpenAI.

---

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: [Streamlit](https://streamlit.io/)
- Backend/Logic: Python (Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib)
- AI: Azure OpenAI with Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG)
- Data Sources:
  - CSO (Central Statistics Office) Earnings Data
  - Yahoo Finance API
  - Kaggle (risk profiling dataset)
  - Irish State Pension data

---

